```

This tool is the only valid way to replay the application.

**IMPORTANT**: You MUST NOT run the application in any other way, e.g. running the binary directly. All invocations must be mediated by the replay tool.

**IMPORTANT**: After modifying source code, you must rebuild the application from source. You will need to:

1. **Analyze the build system**: Examine the source code in /rlenv/source/ to identify the build system being used in order to properly build the application.

2. **Rebuild the application**: Execute the build commands to compile your patched code:
   - Change to the appropriate source directory
   - Run the build commands
   - Ensure build completes successfully without errors
   - **CRITICAL**: Make sure build artifacts are installed to their expected locations
     - The replay tool expects the executable at: /repo/build/test_yuv_rgb
